				p Like if you agree
				p.m-b-0.semi-bold.text-master.font-montserrat.bold $0.00
				p.m-b-0.text-master.fs-12 Description here
				ul.list-unstyled.list-inline.no-margin
						li
							a.text-master(herf='#')
